videos.description: Sean Miller argues another call with the referees who have had enough, slam Miller with a 2nd technical foul and an ejection from the game for Arizona.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Arizona's Sean Miller gets his 2nd technical and is ejected from the game) 2020/02/29 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Arizona's Sean Miller gets his 2nd technical and is ejected from the game

videos.description: Zeke Nnaji reels in the pass from Nico Mannion, turns and crushes home the dunk for Arizona.
videos.headline: Arizona's Nnaji gets between the defense for the slam dunk

videos.description: Tyger Campbell dribbles his way into the paint and puts the off-balance jumper off the glass to take the lead for UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (UCLA takes lead on Tyger Campbell's first basket) 2020/02/29 ESHEETS

videos.headline: UCLA takes lead on Tyger Campbell's first basket
